    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-stellar\">single-use</span> device for locating the wreckage of starships in deep space.<br><br>Select the Rangefinder and <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Scan for Debris</span> (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>) to begin the location process.",
