    "TraditionalChinese": "在深空中尋找太空船殘骸的裝置，只能<span class=\"name name-stellar\">單次使用</span>。<br><br>選擇測距儀並<span class=\"name name-stellar\">掃描殘骸 </span> (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>) 即可開始定位。"
